{"tid":2433885,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"祖國︱英國修例允BNO簽證持有人極貧困下申領資助 另設廣東話專線","createTime":"2021-03-05T07:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T04:09:12.000Z","uid":227801,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1ebd29bb799dc703f96e2b43638b190098a36425","tid":2433885,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210305/EM6ZOEX46NFNFPH7TWFYV2KHI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210305%2FEM6ZOEX46NFNFPH7TWFYV2KHI4%2F&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUrPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=650bdca6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210305%2FEM6ZOEX46NFNFPH7TWFYV2KHI4%2F&h=e01202d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210305/EM6ZOEX46NFNFPH7TWFYV2KHI4/</a><br />\n<br />\nBNO留英計劃「5+1」方案1月31日起於英國政府網站開放登記，不少港人討論去留，惟擔心難以找到工作維生。根據英國內政部近日發佈一份文件，當地政府將修訂移民入境規例，如申請人處於極度貧窮或即將面臨極度貧窮、面對特別低收入等情況，英政府可容許申請人申領政府資助。內政部近日亦推出香港時間「朝9晚5」廣東話專線和電郵，方便港人就簽證問題作查詢。<br />\n<br />\n根據英國內政部於當地時間3月4日發佈一份文件顯示，當地政府將修訂移民入境規例，可按個案情況容許BNO申請人申領政府資助，包括處於極度貧窮或將面臨極度貧窮、面對特別低收入或因極低收入而影響扶養孩子等情況，英政府可豁免其「不得申領政府資助」的限制。多次向英國政府表達關注BNO簽證人或面對經濟問題的當地港人組織「英國港僑協會」在Facebook發文回應指，對英國政府回應訴求，「基於一貫『救生艇』政策扶恤草根家庭」，該會由衷表示支持及感謝。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"b7d8375fc4e538aad3ff05970b8f6eb7ae4e5333","tid":2433885,"uid":21545,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:29:59.000Z","msg":"CLS國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9806869f35407217e14bf236569628ff5520c359","tid":2433885,"uid":58841,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07